        <item>
            <title>三排座椅大型电动 SUV   Hyundai IONIQ 9 路测谍照曝光</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/10/30/hyundai-ioniq-9-suv-spy-photo-video/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=hyundai-ioniq-9-suv-spy-photo-video</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/10/30/hyundai-ioniq-9-suv-spy-photo-video/life-tech/auto/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[唐美凤]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Wed, 30 Oct 2024 05:00:06 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[汽车科技]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Hyundai IONIQ 9]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1272201</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>专门报导电动车消息的网站 Electrek 日前报导，韩国品牌 Hyundai 的大型电动 SUV IONIQ 9 开始在路面实测，并且被媒体拍摄到谍照而提前曝光。高阶定位的 IONIQ 9 是 Hyundai 首款拥有三排座椅的电动 SUV，报导还同时提供了新车的内栊照片，可以见到空间相当充裕。</p><p><span id="more-1272201"></span></p><p>Hyundai IONIQ 9 是基于 2021 年发布的 SEVEN 概念车，新车将会在 11 月举行的洛杉矶车展正式发表。IONIQ 9 的外观设计前衞而独特，配备具有系列特色的 LED 灯条，还有极具线条感的车身轮廓。虽然无法从谍照知道 IONIQ 9 的实际车身尺寸，但预计会跟 KIA 的 EV9 大型电动 SUV 接近。</p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_72413"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/XU7qQGCX7ZA?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p>从曝光的内栊照片可见，IONIQ 9 的第二排腿部空间十分宽敞，估计超过 42 吋，比起竞争对手如 Land Rover 等的空间更加充裕。据悉，IONIQ 9 采用 Hyundai 的 E-GMP 电动车平台，目前已经在 Hyundai 的韩国牙山厂房进行试产，并作最终的质量检测。</p><p><a href="https://unwire.hk/?attachment_id=1272217" rel="attachment wp-att-1272217"><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1272217" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/10301b-694x391.jpg" alt="Hyundai IONIQ 9" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/10301b-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/10301b.jpg 1080w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>资料及图片来源：<a href="https://electrek.co/2024/10/28/hyundai-ioniq-9-spotted-big-body-spacious-interior-images/">electrek</a></p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/10/28/hyundai-kona-mauna-loa-limited-edition/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">韩国 Hyundai Kona 电动车，越野版 Mauna Loa 日本限量发售</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/10/17/hyundai-inster-cross-announced/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Hyundai Inster 发表后获好评，厂方加推户外风格 Cross 版本</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/10/07/hyundai-inster-price-announcement/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">韩国 Hyundai Inster 电动小车，进军国际市场售价曝光</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/10/30/hyundai-ioniq-9-suv-spy-photo-video/life-tech/auto/">三排座椅大型电动 SUV   Hyundai IONIQ 9 路测谍照曝光</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
