        <item>
            <title>M4 Mac mini 终于全面更新设计　尺寸比上代细一半 + 正面增设 USB-C 更实用</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/10/30/mac-mini-m4/notebook/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=mac-mini-m4</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/10/30/mac-mini-m4/notebook/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[蓝骨]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 29 Oct 2024 16:00:40 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[流动电脑]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[M4 Mac mini]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1272187</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>Apple 之前预告过「整个星期」都会有新 Mac 推出，继 iMac 之后第二款更新到 M4 晶片的就是 Mac mini，相对于 iMac，Mac Mini 的更新则相当全面，除了处理晶片外，连外观都有变化。<br /><span id="more-1272187"></span></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1272190" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/design_purpose__ebzr-694x446.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="446" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/design_purpose__ebzr-694x446.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/design_purpose__ebzr.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>Mac mini 上次更新已经是去年 1 月改用 M2 晶片（上图左），今次跳过 M3 直上 M4 晶片，就连外观也有变化，从沿用多年的「月饼罐」设计变成细小但比较厚身的外形，机身只有 5 x 5 吋，比上代细小一半，正面增设两个 USB-C 和耳筒插口，背面亦有 3 个 Thunderbolt（USB-C）插口、HDMI、LAN 插口以及电源。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1272193" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/2d_pb_hand__crjyfo12-694x321.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="321" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/2d_pb_hand__crjyfo12-694x321.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/2d_pb_hand__crjyfo12.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1272191" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/screenshot20241030at-694x399.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="399" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/screenshot20241030at-694x399.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/screenshot20241030at.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>硬件方面，改用 M4 的 Mac mini，效能比 M1 最高可提升 1.8 倍、GPU 效能最快可提升 2.2 倍，支援最多连接 3 个萤幕。而 M4 Pro 型号则在提升效能之外，Thunderbolt 插口更升级到 Thunderbolt 5。有趣的是，开关俾安排在底部，也就是说要将 Mac mini 托起一点才能开机。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1272192" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/2d_bottom__fbzecpbfa-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/2d_bottom__fbzecpbfa-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/2d_bottom__fbzecpbfa.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>新 Mac mini 即日起在 Apple 网上商店开放预订，11 月 8 日正式发售，M4 版本售价由港币 4,599 元起。使用 M4 Pro 的型号则由 10,599 起。一如以往，滑鼠、触控板或键盘都不会随机附送。</p><p>来源：<a href="https://www.apple.com/hk/newsroom/2024/10/apples-all-new-mac-mini-is-even-more-mighty-and-more-mini/">Apple</a></p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/10/29/apple-magic-trackpad-usb-c/parts/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Apple 更新 Mac 周边配件　Magic Trackpad 等全线改用 USB-C</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/10/26/m4-macbook-air-production-beginning-soon/notebook/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">M4 版 MacBook Air 短期内投产，新版 Mac Studio 传押后推出</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/10/25/apple-teases-week-of-mac-announcements-starting-on-monday/software/mac-os-x/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Apple 将发表 M4 Mac 产品 　外媒预计：MacBook Pro + Mac Mini + iMac</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/10/30/mac-mini-m4/notebook/">M4 Mac mini 终于全面更新设计　尺寸比上代细一半 + 正面增设 USB-C 更实用</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
            <wfw:commentRss>https://unwire.hk/2024/10/30/mac-mini-m4/notebook/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
